      • getVersionHandler

        protected static IFXGVersionHandler getVersionHandler(FXGVersion fxgVersion)
        Returns the IFXGVersionHandler for the FXGVersion specified. Note that FXGVersionHandlers are matched first for an exact match. If exact match is not found, then a handler with the same major version is returned.
        Parameters:
        fxgVersion - The FXG version as a FXGVersion.
        Returns:
        The FXG version handler.

      • getVersionHandler

        Parameters:
        version - The FXG version as a double.
        Returns:
        The FXG version handler.
